182 which such individual is a member; and
183 (2) Notwithstanding any options provided under 7 CFR
184 Section 273.11(c)(3), not prorate or exclude the income or
185 financial resources of ineligible individuals under
186 subsection 1 of this section. All such income and resources
187 shall be fully considered.
